Traineeship Description:
This position reports to the Product Manager and interfaces with company managers and staff. SIMTRUM is a venture-funded, e-commerce business in the photonics industries that is disrupting the traditional retail and ecommerce business models using an innovative, hybrid commerce approach. The company boasts of an unmatched team with well-known names from technology, global consumer brands and retail. At the core, it is a young-minded company with a great, flexible working environment, respect for individual and team contribution, and a zeal for achieving the impossible.

Specific Responsibilities:
Trainee to be involved in:
 Assist product manager to prepare and control product specification drawing etc.
 Design and outsource product packaging for assigned product line
 Assist product manager to alliance with supplier for product information, stock level, and quality control document etc.
 Simple mechanical design or existing product modification, rendering product feature image
Maintain product contents on ecommerce website.

Technical Skills and Competencies Trainee will learn during SGUnited Traineeship Programme:
1. Mechanical design skills
2. Physics, engineering, photonics knowledge
3. Programing skills